\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1  wagon house, it was Salavan\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s, but it was as good as his. Thanked the dead god Solraheen for planning all this for him. Cart laden with dead bodies, each of them artists, but that was not his concern.  for the pittering rain as the evening sun. Thankful for the high vantage point over, rut of habit. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Quick!\u8221\'94  \u8220\'93Bring the shit! Before his Spark fades!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Carries the body.}
